Build instructions
==================

- Create directory build
	$ mkdir -p ./build
- Change to build directory
	$ cd build
- Run cmake to create makefiles
  -- Linux, MacOS
	$ cmake ..
  -- MSYS2
	$ cmake -G "MSYS Makefiles" ..
- Compile and link
	$ make
- Install
  -- Linux, MacOS
	$ sudo make install
  -- MSYS2
	$ make install

